<abstract><t>This document specifies public key certificate enrollment procedures authenticated with application-layer security protocols suitable for Internet of Things deployments.  The protocols leverage existing IoT standards including Constrained Application Protocol (CoAP), Concise Binary Object Representation (CBOR) and the CBOR Object Signing and Encryption (COSE) format.</t></abstract>

